---json
{
  "layout": "layouts/t-mofu.njk",
  "permalink": "/accounting/industries/fitness/",
  "slug": "acctind-fitness",
  "tierClass": "section--tier-guide",
  "bodyClass": "page--mofu",
  "callBar": true,
  "title": "Fitness Studio &amp; Gym Accounting: Membership Revenue, Packages, MindBody, Franchise · TechBrot",
  "description": "Specialist accounting for U.S. gyms, boutique studios, and personal training — membership revenue recognition under ASC 606, class packages as deferred revenue, MindBody/Mariana Tek/Glofox integration, LTV/CAC tracking, boutique franchise overlay. Certified ProAdvisors.",
  "breadcrumb": [
    { "name": "Home", "href": "/" },
